In [181]:
def plot_null_values(df):
    null_values = (round((df.isnull().sum() / len(df.index)) * 100, 2)).sort_values(ascending=False)
    
    if null_values.head(2)[1] == 0:
        print("No null values in this dataframe")
    else:
        plot_null = null_values.head(len([i for i in pd.isnull(df).sum() > 0 if i == True]))
        pd_null = pd.DataFrame(plot_null, columns=["% of null values"])
        sns.set(rc={'figure.figsize': (15, 8)})
        sns.set_style(style='white')
        sns.set_palette("Oranges")
        plt.title('Null values')
        plt.ylabel("Features")
        ax = sns.barplot(y=pd_null.index, x='% of null values', data=pd_null, palette="Oranges")
        ax.bar_label(ax.containers[0])

plot_null_values(df)

df1= df.copy()
df1['count'] = 1

df_grouped = df1.groupby(['occasion', 'product']).count().reset_index()
pivot_table = pd.pivot_table(df_grouped, values='count', index='product', columns='occasion', fill_value=0)

f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(14, 6))
cmap = sns.color_palette("Oranges")

ax = sns.heatmap(pivot_table, annot=True, fmt="d", linewidths=.5, ax=ax, cmap=cmap)
ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45)
ax.set_xlabel('Occasion')
ax.set_ylabel('Product types')
ax.set_title('Heatmap of Jewelry Preference by Occasion')
plt.show()
In [101]:
chart_data = df[['price', 'listprice']].copy()
chart_data.sort_values('price', inplace=True)
chart_data.rename(columns={'price': 'x'}, inplace=True)
chart_data = chart_data.groupby('x')['listprice'].count().reset_index(name='listprice|count')


chart = go.Scattergl(
	x=chart_data['x'], y=chart_data['listprice|count'], mode='markers', opacity=0.7, name='all',
	marker={'size': 15, 'line': {'width': 0.5, 'color': 'white'}, 'color': 'darkorange'}
)

figure = go.Figure(
    data=[chart],
    layout=go.Layout({
        'legend': {'orientation': 'h', 'y': -0.3},
        'title': {'text': 'Count of listprice by price'},
        'xaxis': {'title': {'text': 'price'}},
        'yaxis': {'tickformat': '0:g', 'title': {'text': 'Count of listprice'}, 'type': 'linear'}
    })
)

figure.show()
